              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Absolute normalization of c-s ratio was done by thermal",
                "column of BR-10 reactor ( ratio of thermal to",
                "epithermal neutrons - 1.E-4 ); temperature  of neutron",
                "spectrum was estimated by Au filter transmission and",
                "was found to be 27+-11 deg. Ratio of U-233/U235 c-s",
                "for Maxwellian spectrum of temperature 20 deg was taken",
                "as 0.9293 from REL-REF of H.Lemmel."
              ]
